<subSubSection id="C3485ED60947B21FEC95F87725474AD0" lastPageId="21" lastPageNumber="472" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BED0D5D0947B219EC95F87722CE4DC0" blockId="19.[151,1437,1962,2025]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">
<emphasis id="B926D14F0947B219EC95F87721294DEC" bold="true" box="[151,290,1963,1989]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">Etymology:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C5276DE0947B219ED28F877217B4DEC" authorityName="Hamilton" authorityYear="1822" box="[298,368,1963,1989]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cyprinidae" genus="Garra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cypriniformes" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B926D14F0947B219ED28F877217B4DEC" box="[298,368,1963,1989]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">Garra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: named based on a vernacular Indian name, a fish living in mud; 
<taxonomicName id="4C5276DE0947B219E85EF87624A64DED" authorityName="Kirchner, Kruckenhauser, Pichler, Borkenhagen &amp; Freyhof" authorityYear="2020" box="[1116,1197,1962,1988]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cyprinidae" genus="Garra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cypriniformes" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="shamal">
<emphasis id="B926D14F0947B219E85EF87624A64DED" box="[1116,1197,1962,1988]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">shamal</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: the Arabic word for north, for its distribution range in northern 
<collectingCountry id="F3454DCD0947B219EE7BF81322CA4DC0" box="[633,705,1999,2025]" name="Oman" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">Oman</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
